ComicInfo.Summary: THE ROAD LESS TRAVELED, In this shocking epilogue to the "Players and Pawns" (part 6 of 6) storyline, Brandon Jerwa and Tim Seeley take us on a journey to the edge of one man's very existence. This is the story that people will be talking about for a long time to come... are you prepared? Find out when we walk upon "The Road Less Traveled!" Plus! The Wraith 3-part back-up story reaches its finale in this issue! Created by Jerwa and designed by Superman and Aspen artist, Talent Caldwell, the mysterious new villain Wraith is destined to shake up the G.I. Joe universe! Don't miss out on the final chapter of Wraith's debut!
